<section class="endorsement">
  <div class="endorsement-inner reveal">
    <blockquote class="endorsement-quote">
      <p>"Recommended as a reference by <strong>PortSwigger</strong>, the creators of Burp Suite."</p>
    </blockquote>
    <p class="endorsement-context">
      On <a href="/books"><em>Burp Suite Essentials</em></a> — one of two security books I've written.
      I also co-founded <a href="https://null.community" target="_blank" rel="noopener">null</a>, India's open security community, and ran it across 6 cities for 11 years.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .endorsement { padding: 3rem var(--gutter); }

  .endorsement-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 5%, var(--color-surface));
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
  }

  .endorsement-quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .endorsement-quote strong {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .endorsement-context {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .endorsement-context a {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-border-light);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .endorsement-context a:hover {
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
